Class Villager

  • java.lang.Object
    • ue5.Villager
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.util.Comparator<Villager>, IMovable

    public class Villager
extends java.lang.Object
implements IMovable, java.util.Comparator<Villager>
    The class Villager describes one Villager. It must have a name, a gender and an age.
    Author:
    Paul Jureschek, Michael Kinzkofer
